Color Dashboard Data with Themes and Palettes

Customize the colors in your dashboard by choosing a light or dark theme and one of 14 color palettes.

Themes and color palettes help you organize and curate data in your dashboard.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS

Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Essentials, Group (View Only), Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

To set dashboard color themes and palettes:

Change Dashboard Colors
Edit a dashboard.

From Dashboard Theme, choose Light or Dark.
From Dashboard Palette, choose one of 14 color palettes. Wildflowers is the default color palette. If you need an accessible color palette, choose Mineral.

Save the dashboard.
title: Customizing Dashboard Colors with Themes and Palettes
